      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Starting with RenderMan for Blender 27.0, there are now two modes for light linking. The first mode, which is on by default, relies on the RenderMan<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFB27/pages/544637371/Light+Linking+Editor\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637371\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"> Light Linking Editor</a>. The second mode uses Blender’s  native light linking workflow (see the Blender docs, <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://docs.blender.org/manual/en/latest/render/lights/light_linking.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>). Note, the native workflow requires Blender 4.1 and above. </p><h2 id=\"LightLinking-NativeWorkflow\">Native Workflow</h2><p>In order to use the native Blender light linking with RenderMan for Blender, change the Workflow setting under Light Linking in the render properties tab to Blender, as shown in the image below:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"render_properties_light_linking.png\" width=\"396\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/render_properties_light_linking.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754591185189&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=367\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546766879/render_properties_light_linking.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754591185189&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"367\" data-width=\"396\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"547029014\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"render_properties_light_linking.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546766879\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"0a2ac241-8fca-4944-b654-56e6ceccb5d7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/render_properties_light_linking.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754591185189&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=367 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/render_properties_light_linking.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754591185189&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=367 1x\"></span><h2 id=\"LightLinking-Example\">Example</h2><p>Here’s a simple scene with a Suzanne model, a torus, and a three point lighting set up.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"light_linking_native_1.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754593646203&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=356\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546766879/light_linking_native_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754593646203&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"987\" data-width=\"2105\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546963489\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_native_1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546766879\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"bd1c2c77-b8a0-4b7b-a960-cfd2e026921d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754593646203&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=712 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754593646203&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=356 1x\"></span><p>We can start light linking the key light (in our example, it’s named PxrDiskLightShape1) by going to the light’s object properties and looking under Shading → Light Linking</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"light_linking_native_3.png\" width=\"446\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754593782854&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=446&amp;height=596\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546766879/light_linking_native_3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754593782854&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"596\" data-width=\"446\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546963496\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_native_3.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546766879\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"72954938-1401-4f0f-9ef0-a286cbae445c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754593782854&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=446&amp;height=596 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754593782854&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=446&amp;height=596 1x\"></span><p>Creating the collection will immediately turn off lighting for all objects in that scene for this light.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"light_linking_native_4.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754593844127&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=358\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546766879/light_linking_native_4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754593844127&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"995\" data-width=\"2110\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546996258\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_native_4.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546766879\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5c685a28-63e9-4e85-8711-a03868c33286\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754593844127&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=716 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754593844127&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=358 1x\"></span><p>Now, if we want to link this light with the Suzanne model, we can drag and drop the Suzanna object from the outliner to the light linking collection.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"light_linking_native_5.png\" width=\"452\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_5.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1754593955807&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=452&amp;height=645\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546766879/light_linking_native_5.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1754593955807&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"645\" data-width=\"452\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546766891\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_native_5.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546766879\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"17c5939a-53a7-4d42-ba5c-fb742df57a34\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_5.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1754593955807&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=452&amp;height=645 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_5.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1754593955807&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=452&amp;height=645 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"light_linking_native_6.png\" width=\"439\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_6.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1754593965664&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=439&amp;height=555\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546766879/light_linking_native_6.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1754593965664&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"555\" data-width=\"439\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546766897\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_native_6.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546766879\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"811fcca8-98f6-43a1-a283-5c274fe86c2a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_6.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1754593965664&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=439&amp;height=555 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_6.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1754593965664&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=439&amp;height=555 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>And, here you can see the light now only illuminates the Suzanne model.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"light_linking_native_7.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_7.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754594061197&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=359\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546766879/light_linking_native_7.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754594061197&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1006\" data-width=\"2124\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546766909\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_native_7.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546766879\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d770c96c-77f4-45e4-a10f-6180b398aae9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_7.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754594061197&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=718 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546766879/light_linking_native_7.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754594061197&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=359 1x\"></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
